Currently JIRA shows all plugins in the system.  However its not easy to find out what those plugins contribute to the system.

I propose we have a system info / start up logging section that shows plugins points and then lists the classes that implement each plugin point and the plugin that is contributing it.

This is really a support related improvement to help work out what is inside the system.

